@startuml Indian Tax Analysis System - Data Flow Diagram

!theme cerulean
skinparam actorStyle awesome

title Indian Tax Analysis System - Data Flow Diagram\n(Complete Data Movement Visualization)

' ==========================================
' ACTORS
' ==========================================
actor "Taxpayer\n(User)" as user #LightBlue
actor "System Admin" as admin #LightCoral

' ==========================================
' EXTERNAL ENTITIES
' ==========================================
cloud "Google Gemini\nAI Platform" as gemini #LightPink
cloud "Google OAuth\n2.0" as oauth #Orange
cloud "Government\nWebsites" as gov #LightGreen

' ==========================================
' PROCESSES
' ==========================================
package "Frontend Processes" #E8F5E9 {
    usecase "P1: User\nAuthentication" as p1
    usecase "P2: Tax Data\nInput & Validation" as p2
    usecase "P3: Data\nVisualization" as p3
    usecase "P4: File\nUpload" as p4
}

package "Backend API Processes" #E3F2FD {
    usecase "P5: Request\nRouting" as p5
    usecase "P6: Data\nValidation" as p6
}

package "Agent Processes" #FCE4EC {
    usecase "P7: Tax\nCalculation" as p7
    usecase "P8: Fraud\nDetection" as p8
    usecase "P9: AI Chat\nProcessing" as p9
    usecase "P10: Transaction\nAnalysis" as p10
    usecase "P11: Rule\nGeneration" as p11
}

' ==========================================
' DATA STORES
' ==========================================
database "D1: Browser\nLocalStorage" as d1 #FFF9C4
database "D2: Tax Rules\nJSON Files" as d2 #FFE0B2
database "D3: Agent State\n(Memory)" as d3 #E1BEE7
database "D4: Temp Files" as d4 #B2DFDB

' ==========================================
' DATA FLOWS
' ==========================================

' User Authentication Flow
user --> p1 : [Login Credentials\n/ Dev Mode Request]
p1 --> oauth : [OAuth Request]
oauth --> p1 : [JWT Token]
p1 --> d1 : [User Session Data]

' Tax Calculation Flow
user --> p2 : [Income Data:\n- gross_income\n- regime\n- deductions]
p2 --> p5 : [UserFinancialData JSON]
p5 --> p6 : [Validate Request]
p6 --> p7 : [Validated Tax Data]
d2 --> p7 : [Tax Slabs,\nDeductions,\nRebates]
p7 --> p8 : [Tax Calculation Result]
p8 --> p5 : [Combined Result:\n- tax_calculation\n- fraud_analysis]
p5 --> p2 : [API Response]
p2 --> d1 : [Store Results]
d1 --> p3 : [Cached Data]
p3 --> user : [Charts, Stats,\nBreakdown]

' Chatbot Flow
user --> p9 : [User Question]
d1 --> p9 : [User Tax Context]
d3 --> p9 : [Conversation History]
p9 --> gemini : [Prompt + Context]
gemini --> p9 : [AI Response\n(Streaming)]
p9 --> d3 : [Update History]
p9 --> user : [Formatted Response\n(Markdown)]

' Transaction Analysis Flow
user --> p4 : [CSV/Excel File]
p4 --> p5 : [File Upload\n(multipart/form-data)]
p5 --> d4 : [Save Temp File]
d4 --> p10 : [File Path]
p10 --> gemini : [Sample Data +\nSummary Prompt]
gemini --> p10 : [AI Analysis:\n- Insights\n- Tax Implications]
p10 --> p5 : [TransactionAnalysis]
p5 --> d4 : [Delete Temp File]
p5 --> user : [Analysis Results]

' Rule Generation Flow
admin --> p11 : [Generate Rules\n(regime, FY)]
p11 --> gov : [HTTP Crawl]
gov --> p11 : [HTML Content]
p11 --> gemini : [Extract Rules\n(with Google Search)]
gemini --> p11 : [Structured JSON]
p11 --> d2 : [Write Rules File]
p11 --> admin : [Generation Status]

' ==========================================
' DATA ENTITY DESCRIPTIONS
' ==========================================
note right of d1
    **Browser LocalStorage**
    - User session info
    - Tax calculation results
    - Regime preference
    - Last calculation timestamp
end note

note right of d2
    **Tax Rules JSON Files**
    - india_tax_2024_25_old.json
    - india_tax_2024_25_new.json
    Contains: slabs, deductions,
    rebates, surcharges, cess
end note

note right of d3
    **Agent Memory State**
    - user_context: Dict
    - conversation_history: List
    - rules: Dict (cached)
end note

note right of d4
    **Temporary Storage**
    - Uploaded transaction files
    - Deleted after processing
end note

@enduml
